OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773861071
OL,3,CDJ and foster sister who abused girls
OL,4,Cafter discos handed more jail time
OL,6,FA DJ and his foster sister who groomed
OL,7,Fand sexually abused young girls they
OL,8,Fmet at discos have been handed more
OL,9,Fjail time after their first
OL,10,Fconvictions were found to be "the tip
OL,11,Fof the iceberg".
OL,13,FDarren Gibson, 56, and Rebecca Kirton,
OL,14,F41, were jailed for 24 years and 12
OL,15,Fyears respectively in 2024 for attacks
OL,16,Fon three teenage girls.
OL,18,FBut Leeds Crown Court heard 12 more
OL,19,Fvictims were discovered after their
OL,20,Ffirst convictions were reported in the
OL,21,Fmedia.
OL,26,@rD@^OUsD@OO]
