OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773861071
OL,3,CDJ and foster sister who abused girls
OL,4,Cafter discos handed more jail time
OL,6,FOn Wednesday Gibson and Kirton, who
OL,7,Fwere in a relationship at the time as
OL,8,Fwell as being foster siblings, were
OL,9,Fgiven more jail time for sexual
OL,10,Foffences including rape, attempted
OL,11,Frape and indecent assault.
OL,13,FGibson was jailed for an additional 12
OL,14,Fyears after pleading guilty to 34
OL,15,Foffences against 12 girls, aged
OL,16,Fbetween 10 and 15, between 1997 and
OL,17,F2005.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
