PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773861071
OL,3,CDJ and foster sister who abused girls
OL,4,Cafter discos handed more jail time
OL,6,FJudge Mushtaq Khokhar said Gibson was
OL,7,Fa paedophile who used his job to gain
OL,8,Faccess to young girls, adding: "It is
OL,9,Frare to come across such a prolific
OL,10,Foffender as you."
OL,12,FKirton was jailed for an additional
OL,13,Fseven years and six months after
OL,14,Fpleading guilty to 14 sexual offences
OL,15,Fbetween 2002 and 2004.
OL,17,FShe was also jailed for an additional
OL,18,Fsix months for contempt of court after
OL,19,Frefusing to attend the sentencing
OL,20,Fhearing.
OL,26,@pD@`OUrD@QO]
