OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773861071
OL,3,CDJ and foster sister who abused girls
OL,4,Cafter discos handed more jail time
OL,6,FThe court heard Kirton, who was in her
OL,7,Flate teens at the time, would often
OL,8,Fbefriend the girls at events in Leeds
OL,9,Fwhere Gibson was performing, and ply
OL,10,Fthem with alcohol so he could abuse
OL,11,Fthem.
OL,13,FSeveral complainants described being
OL,14,Finvited back to Gibson's house where
OL,15,Fthey were sexually assaulted.
OL,17,FChristopher Dunn, prosecuting, said
OL,18,Fthis would sometimes happen with the
OL,19,F"tacit encouragement" of Kirton, and
OL,20,Fsometimes she would participate in the
OL,21,Fabuse.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@UO]
