OL,3,CDJ and foster sister who abused girls
OL,4,Cafter discos handed more jail time
OL,6,FOne woman started being abused by
OL,7,FGibson when she was 14 years old after
OL,8,Fhe kissed her behind a DJ booth at a
OL,9,Flocal club.
OL,11,FTwo complainants said they met Gibson
OL,12,Fat a "crisps and pop night" at a local
OL,13,Fsocial club and were invited back to
OL,14,Fhis house, where Kirton gave them
OL,15,Falcohol and encouraged them to sit on
OL,16,FGibson's knee, where he would abuse
OL,17,Fthem.
OL,26,@tD@FOUtD@[O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/13
