CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773861071
OL,3,CDJ and foster sister who abused girls
OL,4,Cafter discos handed more jail time
OL,6,FOne of these said she had agreed to go
OL,7,Fto the house because of Kirton, and
OL,8,Fhad "felt safe because another girl
OL,9,Fwas there".
OL,11,FAnother woman said she was approached
OL,12,Fby Kirton at a 14th birthday party.
OL,14,FShe said Gibson "made a fuss of her"
OL,15,Fand said she could go to a nightclub
OL,16,Fwith them, even ringing her "mother to
OL,17,Freassure her she was in safe hands".
OL,19,FThe woman said Gibson drove them back
OL,20,Fto his house where Kirton gave her
OL,21,Falcohol.
OL,26,@pD@EOUqD@JO]vD@QOUvD@dO]xD@]OUyD@cO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/13
