OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773861071
OL,3,CDJ and foster sister who abused girls
OL,4,Cafter discos handed more jail time
OL,6,FShe told police that as Gibson started
OL,7,Fto assault her, she looked at Kirton
OL,8,Ffor help, but she "just smirked".
OL,10,FAnother complainant, who was abused by
OL,11,FGibson from the ages of 11 to 14,
OL,12,Fthought she was in a relationship with
OL,13,Fhim, but the abuse stopped when he
OL,14,Ffound out she had stayed in a tent
OL,15,Fwith boys.
OL,17,FThe court heard he strangled her to
OL,18,Funconsciousness and told her it was
OL,19,Fover because she was "soiled goods".
OL,26,@pD@SOUpD@`O]{D@VOU{D@cO]
