OL,3,CDJ and foster sister who abused girls
OL,4,Cafter discos handed more jail time
OL,6,FOne of the victims said she confronted
OL,7,FGibson years later when she saw him at
OL,8,Fan event "being his usual charming
OL,9,Fself" with a girl who was around the
OL,10,Fsame age she had been when he abused
OL,11,Fher.
OL,13,FHer statement, read in court, said:
OL,14,F"It brought it all back and I was so
OL,15,Fscared he was still doing this to
OL,16,Fother children."
OL,18,FThe woman said she "shouted at him in
OL,19,Ffront of everyone" but "nothing came
OL,20,Fof it".
OL,26,@pD@JOUqD@EO]vD@AOUxD@PO]zD@TOU{D@RO]{D@
OL,26,AXOU|D@FO]
