OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773861071
OL,3,CDJ and foster sister who abused girls
OL,4,Cafter discos handed more jail time
OL,6,FShe said: "(Gibson) was well-known and
OL,7,Fpopular in the area, and it felt like
OL,8,Fhe was rubbing it in my face every
OL,9,Ftime I saw him.
OL,11,F"Everyone thought he was a good man,
OL,12,Feveryone wanted to book him for their
OL,13,Fparties.
OL,15,F"It was like no-one saw this other
OL,16,Fside of him... He preyed on the most
OL,17,Fvulnerable children by getting into
OL,18,Ftheir heads and making them believe
OL,19,Fthat what he was doing was normal and
OL,20,Facceptable.
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/13
