PN,36210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773861071
OL,3,CDJ and foster sister who abused girls
OL,4,Cafter discos handed more jail time
OL,6,F"He made adults think he was a good
OL,7,Fman when he was hiding a vile life."
OL,9,FA statement from another of the
OL,10,Fvictims said: "Darren Gibson and
OL,11,FRebecca Kirton were entrusted with my
OL,12,Fsafety on the night I was raped.
OL,14,F"I looked to (Kirton) for help but she
OL,15,Fmade no attempt to stop what was going
OL,16,Fto happen to me... They are both
OL,17,Fsinister, wicked individuals.
OL,19,F"It gives me peace of mind that today
OL,20,Fthey are sat exactly where they need
OL,21,Fto be."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@dO]rD@OOUvD@AOU{D@AOU}D@GO]
