OL,3,CDJ and foster sister who abused girls
OL,4,Cafter discos handed more jail time
OL,6,FOne complainant described Gibson and
OL,7,FKirton as "predators of the worst
OL,8,Fkind, taking their pick of young kids
OL,9,Fattending their local school discos".
OL,11,FAnother woman's statement said: "The
OL,12,Fday I saw (Gibson's) face on the news
OL,13,Fit was like I was living a nightmare.
OL,14,FI didn't know he had done it to anyone
OL,15,Felse."
OL,26,@oD@KOUqD@dO]sD@aOUwD@FO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/13
