CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773861071
OL,3,CDJ and foster sister who abused girls
OL,4,Cafter discos handed more jail time
OL,6,FSenior crown prosecutor Julie Moss
OL,7,Fsaid: "Darren Gibson systematically
OL,8,Fpreyed on young girls over several
OL,9,Fyears, using his position as a DJ at
OL,10,Flocal children's events to target
OL,11,Fyoung children and take advantage of
OL,12,Ftrust placed in him by the local
OL,13,Fcommunity to cover up his criminality.
OL,15,F"Rebecca Kirton was not a passive
OL,16,Fbystander. She actively facilitated
OL,17,FGibson's abuse, helped him access his
OL,18,Fvictims and frequently carried out the
OL,19,Fabhorrent abuse herself.
OL,26,@oD@GOUwD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
