OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773861071
OL,3,CDJ and foster sister who abused girls
OL,4,Cafter discos handed more jail time
OL,6,F"Gibson thought only of himself and
OL,7,Fhis own sexual gratification through
OL,8,Fall of his offending.
OL,10,F"Both he and Kirton showed complete
OL,11,Fdisregard for the devastating and
OL,12,Flasting impact of their actions on
OL,13,Fvery young and clearly vulnerable
OL,14,Fchildren."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
